<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('../partials/head') %>
<body class="page page--<%= pageClass %>">
<%- include('../partials/header') %>
<main id="main" class="main">

  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal" data-reveal>About</p>
      <h1 class="page-hero__title reveal" data-reveal>Faith Based Innovations</h1>
      <p class="page-hero__lead reveal" data-reveal>We build premium local-first software—CFO, Eden, and Ledger—around <%= SITE.steward.name %>, a controlled intelligence layer, not vague “AI.” Nothing here is for sale or download yet; we are building with intent.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose-grid">
      <div class="prose reveal" data-reveal>
        <h2>Parent company, product family</h2>
        <p>CFO, Eden, and Ledger are distinct products. Faith Based Innovations, LLC is the parent brand that sets the bar for design, engineering, and trust.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prose reveal" data-reveal>
        <h2>Local-first by conviction</h2>
        <p>We believe serious work belongs on serious machines. Local-first architecture reduces surprise, improves reliability, and keeps control where it belongs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="prose reveal" data-reveal>
        <h2>In development</h2>
        <p>Each product is under deliberate engineering. CFO, Eden, and Ledger are not available for purchase, preorder, waitlist, or early access—we do not collect emails for updates on this site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>
<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
<%- include('../partials/mobile-nav') %>
<script type="module" src="/src/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
